    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话后新兴货币守住涨势 特朗普讲话后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-won-rebounds-outperforms-steady-em-currency-index</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，决策者在降低利率时应谨慎行事，新兴市场货币因此保持涨势。由于韩国总统尹锡烈迅速撤销戒严令，韩元周三反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-won-rebounds-outperforms-steady-em-currency-index</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
